OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784227704
OL,3,CMeningitis B jabs should be offered to
OL,4,C15-year-olds on NHS, experts say
OL,6,FTeenagers should be offered meningitis
OL,7,FB (menB) booster vaccines on the NHS,
OL,8,Fgovernment advisors have recommended.
OL,10,FThe advice comes after two people died
OL,11,Ffrom an outbreak of the bacterial
OL,12,Finfection in Kent earlier this year.
OL,14,FThe Joint Committee on Vaccination and
OL,15,FImmunisation (JCVI), which gives
OL,16,Fscientific advice to the government,
OL,17,Fsays 15-year-olds should receive the
OL,18,Fjabs and that catch-up programmes
OL,19,Fshould be in place for those who have
OL,20,Fnever had the vaccine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
