OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784227704
OL,3,CMeningitis B jabs should be offered to
OL,4,C15-year-olds on NHS, experts say
OL,6,FAround a million Year 13 pupils and
OL,7,Funder-25s who are starting university
OL,8,Fin autumn can get the menB vaccine on
OL,9,Fthe NHS.
OL,11,F"We encourage everyone who is eligible
OL,12,Fto book an appointment online to
OL,13,Freceive the vaccine at a local
OL,14,Fpharmacy, in time for the second dose
OL,15,Fto be received before heading off to
OL,16,Funiversity or college," Professor Wei
OL,17,FShen Lim, chairman of the JCVI, said.
OL,19,FHe said two doses of the vaccine are
OL,20,Fneeded at least 28 days apart for
OL,21,Fprotection against the infection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
