CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784227704
OL,3,CMeningitis B jabs should be offered to
OL,4,C15-year-olds on NHS, experts say
OL,6,FThe Department of Health is
OL,7,Fconsidering these suggestions after an
OL,8,Foutbreak at a university in Kent
OL,9,Finfected 20 students, resulting in two
OL,10,Fdeaths.
OL,12,FThe family of Juliette Kenny, who died
OL,13,Fin the outbreak aged 18, have
OL,14,Fcampaigned for routine access to the
OL,15,FmenB vaccine for young people.
OL,17,FMeningitis B spreads through close
OL,18,Fhuman contact, often in saliva.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
