OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784227704
OL,3,CMeningitis B jabs should be offered to
OL,4,C15-year-olds on NHS, experts say
OL,6,FAccording to the NHS, meningitis
OL,7,Fsymptoms to look out for include a
OL,8,Fbody rash, fever, joint pain, severe
OL,9,Fheadaches and sickness or diarrhoea.
OL,11,FIf you have any of these symptoms,
OL,12,Fcall 999 immediately.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
