CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784227704
OL,3,CMeningitis B jabs should be offered to
OL,4,C15-year-olds on NHS, experts say
OL,6,FThe population is not immune to these
OL,7,Fnew strains; therefore, cases increase
OL,8,Fagain.
OL,10,FThe JCVI's suggestions must be backed
OL,11,Fby the government before the vaccines
OL,12,Fcan be rolled out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
